## Phase 5 Addition — Model Routing

### Concept
Route different query types and doc types to different LLM/embedding models loaded in LM Studio. Improves answer quality without changing the retrieval architecture.

### Proposed Model Assignments

| Query/Doc Type | Recommended Model | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| structured (FIX, BBG) | LLaMA 3.1 8B or smaller | Simple lookup, no deep reasoning needed |
| entity_row (KB, Obsidian) | Qwen3-32B | Longer text, needs reasoning to extract right answer |
| procedural/reference (docs, PDF) | Qwen3-32B | Multi-paragraph reasoning, section navigation |
| image | Qwen2-VL or LLaVA | Vision model for OCR, image description |
| astro (FITS) | Qwen3-32B | Metadata reasoning |
| structured query planner | Qwen3-32B | Complex NLP plan generation |
| chat tab | Qwen3-32B | Multi-turn reasoning |

